@startuml approach2-detailed
title **Approach 2: InMemoryCosmosClient + InMemoryContainer — Query Flow (Detailed)**

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #333
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #999

actor "Test Code" as Test
participant "InMemoryCosmosClient\n(extends CosmosClient)" as Client
participant "ConcurrentDictionary\n<string, InMemoryDatabase>\n(Client._databases)" as DbDict
participant "InMemoryDatabase\n(extends Database)" as DB
participant "ConcurrentDictionary\n<string, InMemoryContainer>\n(DB._containers)" as ContDict
participant "InMemoryContainer\n(extends Container)" as IMC
participant "CosmosSqlParser" as Parser
participant "CosmosSqlQuery\n(AST record)" as AST
participant "InMemoryContainer\n.FilterItemsByQuery()" as Filter
participant "InMemoryContainer\n.EvaluateSqlExpression()" as Eval
participant "InMemoryFeedIterator<T>" as FeedIter
participant "InMemoryFeedResponse<T>\n(extends FeedResponse<T>)" as FeedResp

== Setup ==
Test -> Client ** : new InMemoryCosmosClient(…)

== Get Container (lazy creation) ==

Test -> Client ++ : GetContainer(databaseId, containerId)
Client -> DbDict ++ : GetOrAdd(databaseId, …)
DbDict -> DB ** : new InMemoryDatabase\n(databaseId, client)\n[if not exists — thread-safe\n via ConcurrentDictionary]
DbDict --> Client -- : InMemoryDatabase
Client -> DB ++ : GetOrCreateContainer\n(containerId, partitionKeyPath)
DB -> ContDict ++ : GetOrAdd(containerId, …)
ContDict -> IMC ** : new InMemoryContainer\n(containerId, partitionKeyPath)\n[if not exists — thread-safe]
ContDict --> DB -- : InMemoryContainer
DB --> Client -- : Container
Client --> Test -- : Container (InMemoryContainer)

note over Client
  Subsequent GetContainer() calls with
  same databaseId + containerId return
  the SAME instance — data is shared.
end note

== SQL Query Execution (identical pipeline to Approach 1) ==

Test -> IMC ++ : GetItemQueryIterator<T>(queryText,\n  continuationToken, requestOptions)
IMC -> Filter ++ : FilterItemsByQuery(queryText,\n  parameters, requestOptions)
Filter -> Parser ++ : Parse(queryText)
Parser --> AST ** : CosmosSqlQuery\n(SelectFields, Where,\n OrderBy, GroupBy, …)
Parser --> Filter -- : return parsed query
Filter -> Filter : GetAllItemsForPartition(requestOptions)\n→ List<string> from in-memory store
Filter -> Filter : AugmentWithComputedProperties()
Filter -> Filter : ExpandFromSource()\n(FROM c IN c.field)
Filter -> Filter : ExpandAllJoins()\n(JOIN expansion)

group WHERE clause evaluation
  Filter -> Eval ++ : EvaluateWhereExpression\n(expr, JObject item)
  note right of Eval
    Recursively evaluates all expression types:
    Literal, Identifier, PropertyAccess,
    IndexAccess, Binary, Unary, FunctionCall,
    Between, In, Like, Ternary, Coalesce,
    Subquery, ArrayLiteral, ObjectLiteral
  end note
  Eval --> Filter -- : bool (include/exclude)
end

Filter -> Filter : ApplyGroupBy() + aggregates\n(COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX)
Filter -> Filter : ApplyOrderByFields()\n(multi-field, ASC/DESC)
Filter -> Filter : TOP / OFFSET+LIMIT
Filter -> Filter : ProjectFields()\n(SELECT projection)
Filter -> Filter : StripComputedProperties()
Filter -> Filter : DISTINCT
Filter -> Filter : UnwrapValueSelect()\n(SELECT VALUE)
Filter --> IMC -- : List<string> (JSON documents)

IMC -> IMC : Deserialize each JSON →\nJsonConvert.DeserializeObject<T>()
IMC -> FeedIter ** : new InMemoryFeedIterator<T>\n(items, maxItemCount, initialOffset)
IMC --> Test -- : FeedIterator<T>

loop while FeedIter.HasMoreResults
  Test -> FeedIter ++ : ReadNextAsync()
  FeedIter -> FeedIter : EnsureItems()
  FeedIter -> FeedIter : Paginate: Skip(offset).Take(maxItemCount)
  FeedIter -> FeedIter : Generate continuation token
  FeedIter -> FeedResp ** : new InMemoryFeedResponse<T>\n(page, continuationToken, headers)
  FeedIter --> Test -- : FeedResponse<T>
end

== LINQ Query Flow (also identical to Approach 1) ==

note over IMC
  GetItemLinqQueryable<T>()
  → GetAllItemsForPartition()
  → Deserialize → .AsQueryable().OrderBy(x => 0)
  → IOrderedQueryable<T> (LINQ-to-Objects)
  → User applies .Where() / .Select() / .OrderBy()
  → .ToFeedIteratorOverridable()
  → InMemoryFeedIteratorSetup.CreateInMemoryFeedIterator<T>()
  → InMemoryFeedIterator<T>
  → ReadNextAsync() → InMemoryFeedResponse<T>
end note

@enduml
